Package org.ejbca.core.model.hardtoken.profiles

Interface IPINEnvelopeSettings

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    EIDProfile, EnhancedEIDProfile, HardTokenProfileWithAdressLabel, HardTokenProfileWithPINEnvelope, HardTokenProfileWithReceipt, HardTokenProfileWithVisualLayout, SwedishEIDProfile, TurkishEIDProfile
    public interface IPINEnvelopeSettings
    Interface containing methods that need to be implemented in order to have a hard token profile contain PIN Envelope settings.
